    "body": "1. ETH has some protection. But i am not sure about EXP and alike. I am pretty sure there is also no protection in ETC. Reason you were not replayed is mainly because the attack is not profitable most of the time. But also because you would have to hack parity code to perform it.\r\n\r\n2. User education is important. But at least i dont assume thet are at this point. Some still send real eth to testnet addresses by mistake...",
